settings.description: BOO!!! again....             Traverse the Haunted House and find the exit
Test some of your skills with the Tanooki Suit in this brief adventure up in the sky!
Mario rides on a dangerous, and frankly tedious journey. Why? Why not? - Prod. Code: 8992-077B, Rel. Date: 11/26/22, 10:27pm
A Klasky and fun Mario Adventure
Hammers are practically everywhere, attacking from all sides! Make sure to avoid them!

Just keep running, and don't stop! Let the triangular blocks guide you!
Difficulty: 2/5

A switch abundance! And surprisingly, you need to use them..

--Intended with any character--
Fed up with Mario beating them up time and time again, all of the enemies turn giganto! Use the starman to blast your way through these larger-than-life foes.
